加密过程：反转 ASC+1 base64 反转 rot13

解密：
```bash
<?php
$miwen="a1zLbgQsCESEIqRLwuQAyMwLyq2L5VwBxqGA3RQAyumZ0tmMvSGM2ZwB4tws"; 
function decode($str){
	$_o=base64_decode(strrev(str_rot13($str)));
	for($_0=0;$_0<strlen($_o);$_0++){
		$_c=substr($_o,$_0,1);
		$__=ord($_c)-1;
		$_c=chr($__);
		$_=$_.$_c;
	}
	return strrev($_);
}

echo decode($miwen);
?>
```
